CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 8, 1959, pg. B9 reads: "Frog Week Events Highlight Gay Social Season"
TitMainTitle: Group, including Leroy Randall seated on left, and Connie Randall holding cigarette, gathered at picnic table at Lovuola's Farm for Junior Mothers night picnic during FROGS week
